The paper deals with 3D medical image segmentation using reinforcement learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of multi-agent reinforcement learning also suggests a potential fit for robotics (cs.RO) and social intelligence (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the exploration space and reward design, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG).
